summary.ar: أضيفي لمسة حيويّة لإطلالتكِ الرياضيّة باعتمادكِ لهذا البنطلون اللّيقنز الجذّاب. مصمم بقصّة سكيني ونمط قوالب ملوّنة متداخل يضيفك جاذبيّة، كما يأتي بخصر مطّاطي ليمنحكِ حريّة وراحة التحرّك بالحصول على هذا البنطلون اللّيقنز الجذّاب، نسّيقيه مع بلوزة قصيرة لاستكمال إطلالتكِ.
summary.en: Hit the gym in style by sporting this pair of full-length leggings. Ideally made for your exercise and yoga sessions, these skinny fit leggings flaunt a seamless colourblocked design and can be worn with a matching crop top for a complete look. Lending a comfortable fit is the board elasticized waistband.

summary.en: Feel excellent body flexibility and comfort with this contemporary pair of leggings by Trendyol. Moreover, well-crafted from cotton fabric, these leggings lend a skin-friendly feel all the time.

summary.en: This garment is treated with bio softeners made from plant-based oils. They are produced through an environment-friendly manufacturing process that ensures lowered carbon footprint and reduced greenhouse emission.

summary.en: These solid skinny leggings get their flair from the elasticated waistband that ensures a custom fit. Designed to ensure optimum comfort during workouts, these ankle-length leggings are easy to slip-on and extremely flattering. Tailored with panels, these mid-rise leggings look best when teamed with a pair of sports shoes.
